<br>
The Hammer of Judgment is vendor-sold in Shadowhaven.  The Hammer of Divinity drops in Luclin (primarily Ssra) or can be researched, and the same with the Hammer of Souls.  The Hammer of Damnation is a spectral parchment hand-in.<br>
<br>
