<br>
SoV &quot;stacks&quot; with a bunch of other haste spells, but the haste component of each do not unless pally self haste is v3 haste, which lucy says it isn't.<br>
<br>
Haste stacking:<br>
<br>
1 spell/song<br>
1 Item<br>
1 v3 (overhaste)<br>
1 quiver (bow only haste)<br>
<br>
You can have multiple effects that give haste (often SoV and another spell or any haste spell plus regular haste bard song) but only the highest percentage haste will take effect for each category. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=138587" target="top">Denamian</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
